.An Akinori MUSHA Aq knu@iDaemons.org
.Sh BUGS
Since a
.Nx
or
.Ox
tag does not contain a path component, when
.Nm
detects a
.Nx
or
.Ox
tag but there is no
.Pa CVS/*
files in the directory, it assumes that it belongs to
.Nx
pkgsrc
or
.Ox
ports.
